  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink67-kilavi">talainiṉṟu oḻukappaṭāniṉṟa parattai puṟaṉuraittāḷ eṉak kēṭṭa talaivi
          talaimakaṉ vantuḻi avaḷ tiṟattārāy niṉṟu oḻukum vāyilkaḷ kēṭpac colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink67">
          <l>maṭava ḷammanī yiṉikkoṇ ṭōḷē</l>
          <l>taṉṉoṭu nikarā veṉṉoṭu nikarip</l>
          <l>perunalan tarukku meṉpa virimalart</l>
          <l>tātuṇ vaṇṭiṉum palarē</l>
          <l>yōti yoṇṇutal pacappit tōrē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">

        <l> The woman you've just taken is a fool. </l>
        <p/>
        <l> They say she is proud of her great beauty – </l>
        <l> [claiming to] rival me</l> 
          <l>[even though] I am no rival of hers. </l>
          <p/>
        <l> Many [men] have dulled her bright forehead and hair – </l>
        <l> more than [there are] bees sucking the pollen </l>
        <l> from blooming flowers. </l>
        <p/>
        <l> OR: Many [women] have dulled [by their superior beauty] her bright forehead
          and hair – </l>
        <l> more than [there are] bees sucking the pollen </l>
        <l> from blooming flowers. </l>
      </lg>

      </div>
    </body>
